    <item>
      <title>Compustar CS6900 Review (2-Way Remote Start &#43; Security)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/compustar-cs6900-as-remote-start-security-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/compustar-cs6900-as-remote-start-security-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Remote start and basic security systems can improve winter comfort and peace of mind when configured correctly.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Useful two-way communication features.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Better convenience in cold-weather starts.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Security integration improves confidence while parked.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install quality is everything; bad installs create reliability issues.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Some older kits vary in compatibility by vehicle trim.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;ProMaster owners wanting practical security + convenience.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Travelers in colder regions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Often yes, if fitment is confirmed and install quality is high.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>CRL T-Vent Windows for ProMaster Review</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/crl-t-vent-windows-for-promaster-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/crl-t-vent-windows-for-promaster-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;CRL T-Vent windows are one of the highest-impact upgrades for crossflow in ProMaster builds.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Major improvement to crossflow and comfort.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Better fresh-air management in hot conditions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Works well with roof fan systems.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install requires confidence and precision cutting.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cost can feel high when combined with fan upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Builders in warm/humid climates.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Anyone frustrated by stagnant cabin air.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes, especially when paired with a quality roof fan.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Kenwood DNX574S Review (Plus Modern Alternatives)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/kenwood-dnx574s-navigation-head-unit-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/kenwood-dnx574s-navigation-head-unit-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The DNX574S has been a known option in van conversions, but age and feature drift matter.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Established brand reliability.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Familiar interface for many builders.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Works well in integrated dash upgrade projects.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Older feature set compared with newer wireless integrations.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Availability can be inconsistent.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Builders who prioritize stable core navigation/media features.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Users comfortable with older UI paradigms.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Conditionally. If priced close to modern alternatives, newer models usually offer better value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Radiant Composite Insulation &#43; Polyiso for Van Builds</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/radiant-technology-composite-insulation-plus-polyiso-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/radiant-technology-composite-insulation-plus-polyiso-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Insulation choices affect comfort, condensation risk, and long-term build durability.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Layered approach can improve thermal performance in mixed climates.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Materials are generally accessible and budget-scalable.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Good fit for phased DIY builds.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install complexity around curves and thermal bridging.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Results depend heavily on air sealing quality.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;DIY builders prioritizing practical comfort over luxury finishes.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;People converting in variable climate conditions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes, when executed carefully. Material choice alone does not fix poor install strategy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
